0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1828:\"<h3>New pricing in effect!</h3>\n<p>Great news:&#160; We have completed the transition to new pricing and services,&#160; and <strong>we are<u> on fire</u>&#160; to deliver you the best “WordPress for Business” content, best support, and best web-building toolkit on the internet – not to mention the most affordable</strong>.&#160; Now you can access all the <strong>WP Encyclopedia</strong> content from just $25; and you can get our premium program <strong>WP Live</strong>, which includes live support from our expert instructors, theme downloads worth $1400, and stock photos, from just $150.&#160; Details here:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpacademy.com/wordpress-training\">http://wpacademy.com/wordpress-training</a> </p>\n<h3>Free Webinar Monday Jan. 28: Thesis 2.0 Theme, Inside &amp; Out</h3>\n<p>Our free webinar for January will be a repeat of “Thesis Theme, Inside &amp; Out”, but redesigned for the new Thesis 2.0 (one of our favorite themes).&#160; In this popular webinar we build out a clone of the WP Academy Member site (that is a Thesis site). Plus adding a slider, changing CSS, and a lot more techy-geeky stuff.&#160; If you have been inside our training, you know why we strongly recommend that you adopt (and learn) a good <strong>Theme framework</strong> for all your sites.&#160; Thesis is one of the best theme frameworks there is.&#160; Come to this webinar and find out why so many people have fallen in love with this theme.&#160; </p>\n<p>Register here for the live event:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www3.gotomeeting.com/register/956710550\">https://www3.gotomeeting.com/register/956710550</a></p>\n<p>or wait for the recording to be released afterwards.&#160; This is a 100% pitch-free presentation.&#160; </p>\n<p> Cheers,</p>\n<p>Marc Beneteau   <br />”Your Small-Biz Web Technology Mentor” </p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_la